{"tid":62541,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"屌喇星，今日打飛機射撚錯人","createTime":"2017-01-01T04:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T07:02:11.000Z","uid":25125,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58f8631222c9d8822635e9ac17a7a92f3d5acf4a","tid":62541,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:18:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n平時一大早起身見到新聞羅鈺文報新聞<br />\n<br />\n我已經&quot;動L&quot;左既小弟弟就想向佢發炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但為求對鈺文BB既尊重<br />\n<br />\n於是我特登谷左五日唔打飛機<br />\n<br />\n諗住一炮過射俾鈺文，俾佢做facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經谷左五日如箭在弦既小弟弟再忍唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n一開電視，鈺文已經係到ready 緊我d面部護理&quot;精&quot;華&quot;液&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用手將小弟弟好似shotgun咁狂chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎顏射佢既時候...你老母<br />\n<br />\n電視突然轉左做689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾億精兵又忍唔住出左一半，收唔撚番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是一路嗌：哎呀，仆街啦，你老母，呀...呀...呀...呀...呀...<br />\n<br />\n就咁我幾億子彈射左落689塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仆街，而家仲好撚興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，早知下次定住個畫面先射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五日既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b063d508075e1552bf5c8bd3ca57d4b71c82eb3","tid":62541,"uid":62172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hehe"},{"pid":"e62b59c3bd19b41af9e5dfad5a9f9f42933f7c20","tid":62541,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:24:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1304865db66d418c87f865b63f36e3e90aea98df","tid":62541,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:27:17.000Z","msg":"嘩師父你真識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d63bad76e1e2b2cc7c38a4f332607a58855634ea","tid":62541,"uid":30653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:35:17.000Z","msg":"下次唔係689 可能係孽瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6fbfbd2079ad75415d04f948d2e743ea67dd5e","tid":62541,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:36:53.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"437ff74008ad12c340eb154a6bf0ec9f331c6940","tid":62541,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"平時會笑柒上面班人<br />\n但唔撚好成日loop高登啲舊文好冇？ 好撚煩"},{"pid":"f7b0cd3104f4a5e5b09e0e5011936c081ceb8a5f","tid":62541,"uid":70292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"old new is so....如果係真事既話，作者真係一個變態仔"},{"pid":"2f83f93a23eb971c41191a0fa55759f622dcac5b","tid":62541,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T04:44:48.000Z","msg":"又回帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b90bb1885a17ab459731ee4303e1924254d920e","tid":62541,"uid":4249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"